Init-box requirements

1. Configure vs-code
    - download vs-code
    - configure vs-code with all extensions

2. configure zsh shell
    - download zsh shell
    - set theme (Whimsy)

3. configure nvim
    - copy configuration from dotfiles repo

4. download apps [optional]
    - spotify
    - chrome
    - ...

5. configure python, c++

the script should have a progress bar feature. should also be modualrized with 
the above different modules. the script should run properly on unix boxes and 
mac. test with vm and mac.
